name: garlic butter
description: perfect on bread
ingredients:
  - butter (slightly salted) - 1 block
  - parsley finely chopper - handful
  - garlic - 10 to 12 cloves
  - black pepper
steps:
  - sit butter at room temperature
  - mince garlic. add to butter
  - chop parsley. add to butter
  - mix
  - wrap as sausage in parchment paper and set in fridge
